caption.p:
Levels of cytokines in the cell supernatants incubated for 24, 48, and 72 h were assayed by ELISA. (a) IL-4, (b) IL-6, (c) IL-8, (d) IL-12, (e) IL-1- β, (f) TNF- α, and (g) NO. Values were expressed as mean ± SD ( n = 6).
∗
P < 0.05 versus the LPS group, and # P < 0.05 versus the crude AL group of the same concentration.
